CodeSystem: DICOM_CodeSystem_BodyPartExamined
Id: dicom-code-system-body-part-examined
Title: "Body Part Examined"
Description: "Body part examined codes extracted from DICOM PS3.16 Table L-1 and L-2. Theyare used to specify the body part examined in a medical imaging study in tags Anatomic Region Sequence (0008,2218) and Body Part Examined (0018,0015)."
* ^caseSensitive = true
* ^content = #complete
* ^experimental = false

* ^version = "2025.?.20251120"



